---
---

<section id="presentation-viewer" class="bg-dark/50 py-24 px-4 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        方案<span class="text-gold">白皮书</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-gold mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        无需下载，直接在线深度研读我们的“企业信息 AI 化”完整技术架构与实施方案。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- PDF Embed Container -->
    <div class="relative w-full aspect-[16/9] bg-black border border-white/10 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden group">
      <iframe 
        src="/Agent_Native_Enterprise.pdf#toolbar=0&navpanes=0&scrollbar=0&view=FitH" 
        class="w-full h-full border-none"
        style="background: #000;"
        title="Agent Native Enterprise Solution PDF"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-full text-white">
          您的浏览器不支持在线预览，请下载查看。
        </div>
      </iframe>
      
      <!-- Premium Overlay for better aesthetics -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none border-[1px] border-gold/20 rounded-2xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-6">
      <a 
        href="/Agent_Native_Enterprise.pdf" 
        target="_blank"
        class="text-gold hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
        </svg>
        全屏阅读模式
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/Agent_Native_Enterprise.pdf" 
        download
        class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors text-sm flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path>
        </svg>
        下载存档版本
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
